The Withings Smart Body Analyzer helps you assess the healthiness of your environment and choices, using your body's own stats. Plus, it syncs your weight, fat composition, heart rate and environment data to a free app. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.
